Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONSERVATION
AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONSERVATION

Title: Establishes a town of Huntington deer management pilot program
Summary: Establishes a town of Huntington deer management pilot program.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to establishing a town of Huntington deer management pilot program; and providing for the repeal of certain provisions upon expiration thereof
